{
  "stem": "3380.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably about 300 people went to Jaworzno.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jaworzno was a concentration camp also that was part of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Let's put it this way-- like a satellite, a satellite camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I got in the death camp in Jaworzno, the first day-- that was probably the afternoon-- I looked at the vicinity around, you know, the-- see what goes on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I tried to talk to people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I've seen they got a cage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In that cage, they had rabbits, domesticated rabbits, what the lagerfuhrer usually used to have for themselves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the skins, they used to dry out that shouldn't spoil-- shouldn't get spoiled.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I looked at this thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I-- for heaven sake.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I could, I could manufacture this thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can know how to tan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because in Lask, before I went in in the-- they shipped us in the camp, they organized a process of making skins what they need for the Russian front-- fur.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I registered myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I start working there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I learned what to do and how to do with those skins.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I have seen this thing, I decided that I'm going to go into the lagerfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I will tell him that I can make a use out of those skins for the dry skins.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm a specialist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I can make good leather-- I mean good fur-- that you could have either for gloves, you could have for, for all kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says-- and he was really surprised to hear, I mean, that, you know, somebody could make a use out of it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were lots of them, maybe about five, six, or 10.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, what about-- what will you need?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What kind of chemicals will you need?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
